snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard in Huge Audience Gathering
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp is a famous USA based actor, producer, and musician. Johnny Depp has a big space in Hollywood due to his excellency in work. Johnny Depp was born in June 9, 1963 in Owensboro, Kentucky, USA and has started his career in Hollywood in 1984.

Amber Heard is a famous USA based actress. Amber Heard has started her acting career in 2004. Amber Heard was born in April 22, 1986 in Austin, Texas, USA.

This video clip relates to both Johnny Depp and Amber Heard
